						<li>You score is based on sweep paths you make across the island. The number on a cell indicate
							both the number of adjacent trapped cells and how many point the cell is worth. </li>
						<li>The longer the path the more points it brings. Cells can be used only once unless as when
							used as a starting point. You have 60 secondes</li>
					</ul>
